Most people use AI like a fancy search engine. The real power is in workflow automation. Here's what I've built:

🧵 Thread:

1/ Price comparison agent: Upload product link → AI crawls 3 platforms + finds coupons → saves me ¥80+ per month

2/ Document organizer: Drop folder with 3000 files → AI sorts by type/date/size → 10 min vs manual 3 hours

3/ Weekly report generator: Friday 5pm dump work notes → structured report in 30 seconds → boss thinks I'm organized

AI isn't about talking. It's about automating the boring stuff so you can focus on what matters.

#AIautomation #Productivity #OpenClaw #DeveloperTools

